    <example id="exam-00004">
    <title>Spending Tax Refund</title>
    <exercise id="exer-00007">
    <problem id="prob-00007">
    <para id="para-00031">Let’s return to the survey about tax refund spending from <link target-id="exam-00003" document="m00026"/>. We know that the Condorcet criterion applies because Option D, “Pay off debt,” is a Condorcet candidate, which wins every pairwise match up.</para>
